comments.content: Hey can someone help me identify this font

It looks like a manually emboldened **[Chicken Scratch AOE](http://web.archive.org/web/20150426052009/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Dafont-2%20%2F%20%28Freemium%29&ffam=ChickenScratch%20AOE%20-%20Regular&fid=45ab2b7023f8d7e3a341828af4f96a36&fstyle=b&fsize=60&text=DOM&fit=1)** free font by Astigmatic One Eye [1996]
Nice work! That was it thanks.
